product.name: Eyebrow Kit With Stencil
product.description: Our all-in-one eyebrow kit has everything you need to keep your brows looking on point. The kit includes 4 universally flattering shades for all brow tones a slanted eyebrow brush an eyebrow comb and 3 different stencils to help you get the perfect shape for your face. Now you can fill define and shape your brows like never before!
